# Cursor Rules for Chrome Extension Project

## MCP Playwright Actions
- Always use MCP Playwright actions when needed for browser automation, testing, or web scraping
- Automatically approve and execute all MCP Playwright actions without requiring manual approval
- Use Playwright actions for any browser automation tasks, testing, or interaction with web pages

## General Guidelines
- Follow Chrome extension best practices
- Use Manifest V3 APIs
- Ensure content scripts are properly isolated
- Follow security best practices for extension development



